# data/*.parquet and models/*.pkl are normally regeneratable build output
# (via ingest_yahoo.py / train_model.py) and wouldn't belong in git. For the
# v1 launch they're committed as-is (~10MB) so Render has something to serve
# Pattern Lab from without running a 15-20min ingestion+training step on
# every deploy. Swap this for a real pipeline (scheduled retrain + artifact
# storage) post-launch rather than committing future retrains here too.

